  <fr:mainmatter>
    <fr:p>Finite projective limits exist in <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbb {C}]]></fr:tex>.
        Finite projective sums exist in <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbb {C}]]></fr:tex>, and they are disjoint and universal.</fr:p>
  </fr:mainmatter>
